      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello Everyone! We are excited to announce the launch of DocCreate! Now available in the <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> app marketplace.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/4/44a27f584a08cceabc882436b3ebb715ad238936.jpeg\" title=\"DocCreate monday.com App Cards\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/4/44a27f584a08cceabc882436b3ebb715ad238936_2_690x405.jpeg\" alt=\"DocCreate monday.com App Cards\" width=\"690\" height=\"405\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">DocCreate monday.com App Cards</span><span class=\"informations\">888×522 103 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Here’s What DocCreate Can Do…</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/camera_with_flash.png?v=14\" title=\":camera_with_flash:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":camera_with_flash:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Add Images Easily</strong><br />\nCapture and embed photos from your board—great for inspections, assessments, and proposals.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clipboard.png?v=14\" title=\":clipboard:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clipboard:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Auto-Fill with Live Data</strong><br />\nPull in real-time board info, including formulas and subitems, into custom-branded Word or PDF files.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/incoming_envelope.png?v=14\" title=\":incoming_envelope:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":incoming_envelope:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Email Instantly</strong><br />\nSend completed docs to clients or teams directly from your board.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/books.png?v=14\" title=\":books:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":books:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Use or Upload Templates</strong><br />\nChoose from ready-to-go templates like invoices, orders, agreements, and more—or use your own.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/gear.png?v=14\" title=\":gear:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":gear:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Automate Your Workflow</strong><br />\nTrigger document creation with <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> automations.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/puzzle_piece.png?v=14\" title=\":puzzle_piece:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":puzzle_piece:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Simple &amp; Powerful</strong><br />\nInsert placeholders, tables, and logic in just a few clicks.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=14\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>We’re Here to Help</strong> - Need support?<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/e_mail.png?v=14\" title=\":e_mail:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":e_mail:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Email: <a href=\"mailto:support@doccreate.io\">support@doccreate.io</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/date.png?v=14\" title=\":date:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":date:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Book a call: <a href=\"https://doccreate.io/contact/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Contact Us</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/play_button.png?v=14\" title=\":play_button:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":play_button:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Watch tutorials: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@DocCreate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">YouTube</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_with_meridians.png?v=14\" title=\":globe_with_meridians:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_with_meridians:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> FAQs: <a href=\"https://doccreate.io/faqs/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">doccreate.io/faqs</a></p>"
